snippet.title: Ymir - (City & Empire Builder Game)[Steam Release]
snippet.description:
Ymir Intro Video: http://bit.ly/2yr27ri
Ymir website: https://ymir-online.com/
Previous Playthrough: Part 1: https://youtu.be/VpUbQRG4y_o

Ymir on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/378360/Ymir/
Ymir is a 4X multiplayer strategy game combined with a city builder where each player develops a civilization of pigmen starting at the stone age.
